I made a To-Do-List app according to the specifications of the the practice prolem
with the following Components and Functionalities:

Input field:
	- Adds inputed text when enter is clicked or the ADD button is clicked

REMOVE ITEMS button:
	- Removes selected item from the list

HIGHLIGHT button:
	- Sets the color in the color input to the selected item
	- Changes all item colors to the default on DOUBLE CLICK

SORT ALPHABETICALLY:
	- Sorts all items alphativally

SORT BY COLOR:
	- Sorts all items relative their hex color